import React from "react";
import Layout from "../../Components/Layout";
import { Container, Form, Row, Col, Button } from "react-bootstrap";
import Input from '../../Components/Layout/UI/Input';

export default function index() {
  return (
    <Layout>
      <Container>
        <Row style={{ marginTop: "50px" }}>
          <Col md={{ span: 6, offset: 3 }}>
            <Form>
              <Row>
                <Col md={6}>
                  <Input
                  label="Full Name"
                  placeholder="FullName"
                  
                  type="text"
                  onChange={()=>{}}
                  />
                
                </Col>
                <Col md={6}>
                <Input
                  label="Date of Birth"
                  placeholder="DOB"
                 
                  type="date"
                  onChange={()=>{}}
                  />
                </Col>
                <Col md={6}>
                <Input
                  label="Address"
                  placeholder="Address"
                  
                  type="text"
                  onChange={()=>{}}
                  />
                </Col>
                <Col md={6}>
                <Input
                  label="Phone Number"
                  placeholder="Phone Number"
               
                  type="text"
                  onChange={()=>{}}
                  />
                </Col>
                <Col md={6}>
                <Input
                  label="Username"
                  placeholder="Username"
                 
                  type="text"
                  onChange={()=>{}}
                  />
                </Col>
                
              </Row>
              <Input
                  label="Email"
                  placeholder="Email"
                  
                  type="email"
                  onChange={()=>{}}
                  />
             

             <Input
                  label="Password"
                  placeholder="Password"
               
                  type="password"
                  onChange={()=>{}}
                  />

              <Button variant="primary" type="submit">
                Submit
              </Button>
            </Form>
          </Col>
        </Row>
      </Container>
    </Layout>
  );
}
